    "rule":  "Bei Modalverben im Perfekt: haben + Infinitiv + Modalverb (Infinitiv, nicht Partizip!).",
    "explanation":  "When modal verbs are used in Perfekt, the Partizip II is replaced by the infinitive, creating a \u0027double infinitive\u0027 at the end: Ich habe kommen müssen.",
